Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.78,0:02:32.28,Place,,0,0,0,,{\pos(95,960)}同區　操縱者宿舍
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.95,0:02:32.24,Default,,0,0,0,,喵喵~
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.57,0:02:35.73,Default,,0,0,0,,你是住在附近的孩子嗎 喵~
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.75,0:02:38.75,Default,,0,0,0,,莓?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.13,0:02:40.33,Default,,0,0,0,,廣 廣?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.33,0:02:42.75,Default,,0,0,0,,不用特地出來迎接我沒關係的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.26,0:02:46.40,Default,,0,0,0,,還不是因為有人一大早就鬧失蹤
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.40,0:02:49.93,Default,,0,0,0,,即使會感到不自在 既然廣最後還是留下來的話
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.93,0:02:51.75,Default,,0,0,0,,那就問心無愧地待在這就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.71,0:02:59.77,Default,,0,0,0,,直美好像平安無事呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.77,0:03:01.55,Default,,0,0,0,,已經轉送到醫院了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.55,0:03:03.11,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 我有聽說
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.84,0:03:07.91,Default,,0,0,0,,那架FRANXX 是廣操縱的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.28,0:03:10.84,Default,,0,0,0,,我不記得了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.97,0:03:12.62,Default,,0,0,0,,所以我想再上去一次
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.62,0:03:14.04,Default,,0,0,0,,想確認是不是真的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.04,0:03:15.37,Default,,0,0,0,,再上去一次...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.55,0:03:17.97,Default,,0,0,0,,可是她不是我們隊伍的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.55,0:03:17.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs40\pos(788.8,980)}002
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.97,0:03:20.55,Default,,0,0,0,,我不在乎 只要能搭上去就好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.26,0:03:22.95,Default,,0,0,0,,我有聽說了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.95,0:03:24.15,Default,,0,0,0,,關於她的傳聞
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.95,0:03:24.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs40\pos(926.5,980)}002
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.26,0:03:26.71,Default,,0,0,0,,至今為止和她搭檔的操縱者
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.71,0:03:29.60,Default,,0,0,0,,沒有一個能與她共同操縱超過三次
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.86,0:03:31.75,Default,,0,0,0,,依然能活著回來的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.00,0:03:37.08,Default,,0,0,0,,雖然不知道是真是假
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.20,0:03:40.15,Default,,0,0,0,,但我想還是別和她有所牽連比較好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.15,0:03:42.13,Default,,0,0,0,,但是 如果我無法操縱FRANXX
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.13,0:03:44.13,Default,,0,0,0,,待在這跟離開又有什麼差別
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.95,0:03:45.93,Default,,0,0,0,,廣...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.20,0:03:50.08,Default,,0,0,0,,喂 廣 你快來看
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.08,0:03:51.93,Default,,0,0,0,,那個人跑來食堂了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.55,0:04:02.04,Default,,0,0,0,,嘔
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.26,0:04:06.64,Default,,0,0,0,,為什麼那傢伙還在這啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.26,0:04:06.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs40\pos(928,980)}002
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.35,0:04:09.14,Name,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1116.667,965)\fs30}Zero Two
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.31,0:04:09.28,Default,,0,0,0,,真特別的人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.60,0:04:11.51,Default,,0,0,0,,應該是因為很喜歡甜食吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.14,0:04:15.26,Name,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,250)\pos(1451.2,965)}心
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.79,0:04:13.06,Default,,0,0,0,,她不算是人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.40,0:04:15.26,Name,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,250)\pos(405.333,960)}未來
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.06,0:04:14.35,Default,,0,0,0,,有這個啊 這個
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.35,0:04:15.28,Default,,0,0,0,,別說那種話
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.56,0:04:20.77,Name,,0,0,0,,{\fad(130,0)\pos(610,960)}莓
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.08,0:04:19.66,Default,,0,0,0,,畢竟是她救了我們的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.17,0:04:24.13,Default,,0,0,0,,繼承了叫龍的血脈這件事 是真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.77,0:04:26.25,Name,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1553.333,960)}生野
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.28,0:04:25.44,Default,,0,0,0,,而且
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.55,0:04:28.73,Default,,0,0,0,,00開頭的代號 照理來說不存在才是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.73,0:04:31.26,Default,,0,0,0,,和傳聞中的形象截然不同耶
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.75,0:04:33.50,Name,,0,0,0,,{\pos(497.333,960)}五郎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.75,0:04:33.50,Name,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1754.667,960)}太
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.95,0:04:34.26,Default,,0,0,0,,看上去是個美人的 真可惜呀
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.62,0:04:37.13,Default,,0,0,0,,明明受了那麼重的傷 卻都痊癒了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.50,0:04:37.96,Name,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1142.667,960)}廣
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.43,0:04:40.73,Default,,0,0,0,,妳的本事我已經充分見識到了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.84,0:04:44.48,Default,,0,0,0,,不嫌棄的話 就由本大爺來當妳的搭檔如何呀
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.25,0:04:44.35,Name,,0,0,0,,{\fad(170,0)\pos(1145.333,960)}揃目
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.48,0:04:46.33,Default,,0,0,0,,比起那個愛哭鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.45,0:04:48.84,Default,,0,0,0,,我肯定能操縱的更好哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.35,0:04:49.35,Name,,0,0,0,,{\pos(893.333,960)}滿
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.01,0:04:51.82,Default,,0,0,0,,下次一起...嗚哇!!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.82,0:04:53.44,Default,,0,0,0,,妳幹什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.53,0:04:56.91,Default,,0,0,0,,啊!!!本大爺所有衣服中最帥的一件呀!!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.88,0:04:59.60,Default,,0,0,0,,妳打算怎麼賠我
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.32,0:05:04.70,Default,,0,0,0,,誒?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.94,0:05:07.06,Default,,0,0,0,,這個 甜甜的很美味唷
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.25,0:05:08.21,Default,,0,0,0,,一起吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.31,0:05:11.88,Default,,0,0,0,,我有事想問妳
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.28,0:05:13.08,Default,,0,0,0,,那個時候...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.23,0:05:15.16,Default,,0,0,0,,我有好好地操縱到最後嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.78,0:05:21.18,Default,,0,0,0,,你表現得很好唷 超棒的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.78,0:05:21.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs40\pos(747.2,980)}操縱
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.62,0:05:22.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Darling
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.08,0:05:26.35,Default,,0,0,0,,D...Darling?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.00,0:05:28.64,Default,,0,0,0,,欸 那是怎樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.64,0:05:29.68,Default,,0,0,0,,我也不是很清楚呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.68,0:05:32.08,Default,,0,0,0,,喂 不准無視我的存在!!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.55,0:05:34.91,Default,,0,0,0,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.08,0:05:36.55,Default,,0,0,0,,果然那時
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.66,0:05:38.42,Default,,0,0,0,,是我操縱的沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.15,0:05:42.02,Default,,0,0,0,,好了好了 先不要吵囉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.02,0:05:43.15,Default,,0,0,0,,七小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.40,0:05:45.37,Default,,0,0,0,,咳咳 那麼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.37,0:05:49.37,Default,,0,0,0,,承繼自花園時期起 照顧你們的任務
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.37,0:05:49.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs40\pos(710.4,980)}Garden
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.82,0:05:54.04,Default,,0,0,0,,我是從APE本部派至第13都市部隊的七
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.33,0:05:56.25,Name,,0,0,0,,{\fad(130,0)\pos(960,960)}APE作戰本部 操縱者管理官 七
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.04,0:05:55.51,Default,,0,0,0,,以後依然請你們多關照囉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.51,0:05:56.75,Default,,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.75,0:05:57.60,Default,,0,0,0,,七姐
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.60,0:05:59.13,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼了 莓?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.28,0:06:01.51,Default,,0,0,0,,她會繼續待在這嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.28,0:06:01.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs40\pos(722.667,980)}002
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.62,0:06:04.73,Default,,0,0,0,,關於Zero Two 目前還在等待本部的指令
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.73,0:06:07.04,Default,,0,0,0,,基本上是和你們分開行動的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.55,0:06:09.40,Default,,0,0,0,,來吧 妳要跟我走唷
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.40,0:06:13.00,Default,,0,0,0,,什麼嘛 我覺得這邊比較舒服說
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.00,0:06:14.53,Default,,0,0,0,,等 等等
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.62,0:06:16.40,Default,,0,0,0,,那個 Zero Two
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.53,0:06:20.15,Default,,0,0,0,,請讓我 再操縱一次妳的FRANXX
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.15,0:06:22.00,Default,,0,0,0,,有件事 我想再確認一次
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.00,0:06:24.51,Default,,0,0,0,,那不是你能逕自決定的事唷
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.51,0:06:27.46,Default,,0,0,0,,大概幾天後爸爸們就會下達對你的指令了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.51,0:06:27.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs40\pos(758.4,980)}賢者
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.73,0:06:29.53,Default,,0,0,0,,在那之前要乖乖的唷
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.53,0:06:30.71,Default,,0,0,0,,爸爸的指令
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.53,0:06:30.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs40\pos(859,980)}賢者
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.77,0:06:32.28,Default,,0,0,0,,為什麼是這傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.35,0:06:36.26,Default,,0,0,0,,是怎樣啊 那傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.75,0:06:40.37,Default,,0,0,0,,您任意行動我會很為難的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.37,0:06:42.73,Default,,0,0,0,,只是和Darling一起用餐而已
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.86,0:06:45.53,Default,,0,0,0,,減少和操縱員的接觸吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.86,0:06:45.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs40\pos(926.4,980)}Parasite
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.53,0:06:48.40,Default,,0,0,0,,對那群孩子來說 妳帶來的刺激太強烈了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.37,0:06:52.62,Default,,0,0,0,,待在這真讓人喘不過氣呀
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.84,0:06:56.86,Default,,0,0,0,,確認於第13都市出現莫霍羅維奇級一架
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.86,0:06:59.26,Default,,0,0,0,,已由鶴望蘭將其消滅
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.26,0:07:02.75,Default,,0,0,0,,燃料儲備率降低至百分之54
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.75,0:07:04.24,Default,,0,0,0,,目前停泊在近郊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.24,0:07:07.24,Default,,0,0,0,,請求與第26都市進行連通的許可
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.24,0:07:07.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs40\pos(1168,980)}Kissing
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.24,0:07:08.44,Default,,0,0,0,,許可
Comment: 0,0:00:01.00,0:00:01.00,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.20,0:07:08.20,Place,,0,0,0,,{\pos(95,960)}APE中央本部會議
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.45,0:07:11.45,Place,,0,0,0,,{\pos(86,960)}『智庫　拉馬克』
Comment: 0,0:00:01.00,0:00:01.00,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.45,0:07:11.45,Comment,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}讓-巴蒂斯特·拉馬克 : 法國人，於1809年發表《動物哲學》一書，\N系統地闡述了他的進化理論，即俗稱的拉馬克學說。\N並認為用進廢退與獲得性遺傳兩個法則是生物產生變異的原因和適應環境的過程。
Comment: 0,0:00:01.00,0:00:01.00,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.44,0:07:12.64,Default,,0,0,0,,了解 連通預計於175小時後開始
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.44,0:07:12.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs40\pos(704,980)}Kissing
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.82,0:07:17.15,Default,,0,0,0,,好像有收到關於讓鶴望蘭留在第13都市的報告呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.82,0:07:17.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs40\pos(885.333,980)}Strelizia
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.15,0:07:19.57,Default,,0,0,0,,那丫頭又在任性了嗎...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.57,0:07:21.66,Default,,0,0,0,,博士再怎麼寵她也得有個限度吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.66,0:07:24.24,Default,,0,0,0,,不過 這次的樣本...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.66,0:07:24.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs40\pos(1105,980)}Case
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.24,0:07:28.51,Default,,0,0,0,,就數據來看目前仍未出現肉體老化的徵兆
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.51,0:07:30.42,Default,,0,0,0,,確實是極為罕見的案例呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.51,0:07:32.15,Default,,0,0,0,,CODE:016...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.15,0:07:33.91,Default,,0,0,0,,就是那個孩子對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.91,0:07:35.04,Default,,0,0,0,,萬萬不可
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.04,0:07:39.15,Default,,0,0,0,,讓她和尚未解析的特殊樣本接觸只會汙染血統
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.26,0:07:41.42,Default,,0,0,0,,應該立刻進行回收
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.48,0:07:45.26,Default,,0,0,0,,不過呢 在那場戰鬥中散發出的光輝
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.26,0:07:47.51,Default,,0,0,0,,值得令人深究
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.95,0:07:49.62,Default,,0,0,0,,再觀察一陣子吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.15,0:07:52.48,Default,,0,0,0,,那頭叫龍
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.48,0:07:54.66,Default,,0,0,0,,真虧你敢正面應戰呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.95,0:07:56.57,Default,,0,0,0,,那是怎樣的感覺?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.95,0:07:59.73,Default,,0,0,0,,當時發生的事 我全都不記得了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.33,0:08:01.20,Default,,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.80,0:08:03.35,Default,,0,0,0,,操縱的感覺卻還殘留著
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.35,0:08:04.53,Default,,0,0,0,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.53,0:08:05.75,Default,,0,0,0,,不管怎麼說
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.75,0:08:08.08,Default,,0,0,0,,你願意留下來我很高興唷
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.08,0:08:10.88,Default,,0,0,0,,廣大概是正式上場時特別強的類型吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.88,0:08:12.33,Default,,0,0,0,,就這樣被你超前了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.33,0:08:14.02,Default,,0,0,0,,閃開 別擋路
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.48,0:08:18.93,Default,,0,0,0,,比我們還早進行實戰什麼的 我絕對不會承認
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.93,0:08:21.00,Default,,0,0,0,,像你這樣的愛哭鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.00,0:08:21.73,Default,,0,0,0,,哼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.24,0:08:24.46,Default,,0,0,0,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.46,0:08:27.37,Default,,0,0,0,,為什麼會做這麼小件啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.37,0:08:28.57,Default,,0,0,0,,超緊的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.57,0:08:30.80,Default,,0,0,0,,連結時的感覺
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.80,0:08:32.91,Default,,0,0,0,,能早點習慣的話就好了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.91,0:08:35.57,Default,,0,0,0,,和在訓練機裡時完全不同
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.28,0:08:38.73,Default,,0,0,0,,就像是發育過熟的身體
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.08,0:08:39.91,Background,,0,0,0,,等等 未來妳
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.73,0:08:42.91,Default,,0,0,0,,被人從內到外翻攪得黏答答的感覺呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.02,0:08:44.53,Default,,0,0,0,,看我的看我的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.53,0:08:46.55,Default,,0,0,0,,別提了 不然我又會想起來
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.55,0:08:48.24,Default,,0,0,0,,有那麼難受嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.44,0:08:50.93,Default,,0,0,0,,雖然確實不太自在
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.93,0:08:52.44,Default,,0,0,0,,不過 為什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.93,0:08:56.15,Default,,0,0,0,,我感受到的是一股安全感
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.53,0:08:58.55,Default,,0,0,0,,彷彿有人陪伴在身邊般
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.55,0:08:59.95,Default,,0,0,0,,誒~
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.95,0:09:01.51,Default,,0,0,0,,好厲害唷
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.51,0:09:04.91,Default,,0,0,0,,要是我的數值能和小莓一樣高就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.91,0:09:07.57,Default,,0,0,0,,一定是因為和五郎默契十足吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.24,0:09:16.02,Default,,0,0,0,,同為代號兩位數的菁英 令人稱羨的情誼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.11,0:09:17.55,Default,,0,0,0,,謝謝妳的讚美
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.55,0:09:20.57,Default,,0,0,0,,說到菁英 那個廣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.57,0:09:22.73,Default,,0,0,0,,不但帶了個女生回來
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.73,0:09:25.86,Default,,0,0,0,,而且還被叫Darling什麼的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.26,0:09:29.17,Default,,0,0,0,,搞不好那兩個人真的能組成搭...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.66,0:09:36.64,Default,,0,0,0,,怎 怎麼了...?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.33,0:09:43.02,Default,,0,0,0,,作戰方針的部分由我來下達指令
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.11,0:09:47.66,Default,,0,0,0,,不過 現場的指揮仍由領隊機翠雀擔任
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.11,0:09:47.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs40\pos(1304,980)}Delphinium
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.75,0:09:48.66,Default,,0,0,0,,了解
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.60,0:09:52.17,Default,,0,0,0,,為什麼是她當隊長啊...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.03,0:09:57.53,Name,,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,960)}APE作戰本部 都市防禦作戰司令官 八
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.22,0:09:57.73,Default,,0,0,0,,那麼 訓練即將開始
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.06,0:10:00.86,Default,,0,0,0,,雖然本次訓練是首次讓各位操縱實機
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.86,0:10:02.40,Default,,0,0,0,,還是請各位毋須慌張 保持冷靜
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.55,0:10:04.62,Default,,0,0,0,,想像將自身完全託付給對方般
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.62,0:10:06.08,Default,,0,0,0,,專注在配合搭檔的一舉一動
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.17,0:10:08.00,Default,,0,0,0,,那麼 連結開始
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.88,0:10:12.77,Default,,0,0,0,,來了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.15,0:10:15.62,Default,,0,0,0,,不要發出奇怪的聲音啦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.62,0:10:17.26,Default,,0,0,0,,我也不想啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.26,0:10:19.42,Default,,0,0,0,,彼此間哪怕有些微的分歧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.42,0:10:21.77,Default,,0,0,0,,都會對能量負載值造成巨大的影響
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.91,0:10:24.75,Default,,0,0,0,,接受並信賴著搭檔 才是最重要的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.93,0:10:28.80,Default,,0,0,0,,還好嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.80,0:10:31.37,Default,,0,0,0,,沒問題 就這樣繼續吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.31,0:10:50.22,Default,,0,0,0,,我該不會操縱的很爛吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.22,0:10:52.17,Default,,0,0,0,,不會的 感覺很好唷
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.72,0:10:56.13,Name,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,130)\pos(644.267,936)\be9}金雀花
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.72,0:10:56.13,Name,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,130)\pos(1488.8,936)\be9}吊蘭
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.80,0:10:55.00,Default,,0,0,0,,我們很合的來呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.42,0:10:58.60,Default,,0,0,0,,喂喂 才這點程度不要在那你儂我儂的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.60,0:11:01.44,Default,,0,0,0,,最快的肯定是本大爺我啦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.30,0:11:01.65,Name,,0,0,0,,{\fad(130,0)\pos(514.667,936)\be9}青葙
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.44,0:11:03.22,Default,,0,0,0,,尤其是那邊的菁英組合
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.44,0:11:03.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs40\pos(1094.667,980)}兩位數
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.22,0:11:04.68,Default,,0,0,0,,給我好好記著吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.85,0:11:02.97,Name,,0,0,0,,{\pos(593.333,936)\be9}翠雀
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.68,0:11:06.06,Default,,0,0,0,,真有精神啊...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.06,0:11:08.15,Default,,0,0,0,,在同伴間分高下沒有意義吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.20,0:11:10.37,Default,,0,0,0,,還在嘴硬啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.31,0:11:14.06,Default,,0,0,0,,等...等一下啦 不要那麼粗魯...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.62,0:11:19.84,Default,,0,0,0,,沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.40,0:11:21.64,Default,,0,0,0,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.95,0:11:24.82,Default,,0,0,0,,操控方面是男生掌握主導權的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.82,0:11:27.71,Default,,0,0,0,,多顧慮一下和FRANXX連結的女生吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.88,0:11:29.48,Default,,0,0,0,,什麼嘛 一副了不起的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.62,0:11:32.04,Default,,0,0,0,,各機體以翠雀為中心
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.62,0:11:32.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs40\pos(992,980)}Delphinium
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.04,0:11:34.06,Default,,0,0,0,,保持陣型前進
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.06,0:11:35.11,Default,,0,0,0,,了解
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.60,0:11:49.24,Default,,0,0,0,,那個時候 我成功操縱了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.60,0:11:53.75,Default,,0,0,0,,要是能再次和Zero Two 一起操縱鶴望蘭的話
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.60,0:11:53.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs40\pos(1395,980)}Strelizia
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.95,0:11:54.95,Default,,0,0,0,,我...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.44,0:12:07.51,Default,,0,0,0,,用實機進行啟動測試是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.50,0:12:12.50,Place,,0,0,0,,{\pos(95,960)}要塞都市內　停機棚
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.95,0:12:15.15,Default,,0,0,0,,連結時的要訣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.15,0:12:16.31,Default,,0,0,0,,要是能再...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.68,0:12:21.24,Default,,0,0,0,,哎 告訴我
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.64,0:12:23.17,Default,,0,0,0,,為什麼會是廣?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.75,0:12:24.71,Default,,0,0,0,,廣?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.71,0:12:26.80,Default,,0,0,0,,妳是指我的Darling嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.80,0:12:28.55,Default,,0,0,0,,又這樣叫他...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.82,0:12:32.22,Default,,0,0,0,,當時妳擊退叫龍的事 我很感謝
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.22,0:12:35.53,Default,,0,0,0,,但希望從今以後妳不要再纏著廣了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.53,0:12:36.57,Default,,0,0,0,,為何?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.57,0:12:38.75,Default,,0,0,0,,妳和我們是不同的部隊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.75,0:12:40.17,Default,,0,0,0,,終究會離開這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.17,0:12:42.51,Default,,0,0,0,,所以請妳不要讓廣抱持著莫名的期待
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.64,0:12:44.04,Default,,0,0,0,,哦~
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.04,0:12:46.48,Default,,0,0,0,,妳是Darling的什麼人?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.77,0:12:48.55,Default,,0,0,0,,我是這個部隊的隊長
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.68,0:12:50.17,Default,,0,0,0,,哦~
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.80,0:12:52.13,Default,,0,0,0,,喂...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.26,0:12:57.46,Default,,0,0,0,,甜甜的味道呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.26,0:12:57.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs40\pos(825,980)}天真
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.71,0:12:59.04,Default,,0,0,0,,我不討厭唷
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.88,0:13:08.00,Default,,0,0,0,,我們真的能挺身而戰嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.55,0:13:10.42,Default,,0,0,0,,以叫龍作為對手
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.80,0:13:13.75,Default,,0,0,0,,像廣那樣操縱著FRANXX戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.75,0:13:17.57,Default,,0,0,0,,啥!? 我就直說了 那根本稱不上操縱吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.57,0:13:20.31,Default,,0,0,0,,測試不合格的那傢伙 怎麼可能成功啟動
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.31,0:13:22.17,Default,,0,0,0,,但事實上啟動了不是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.17,0:13:25.31,Default,,0,0,0,,感覺爸爸們也對廣很中意的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.17,0:13:25.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs40\pos(691.2,980)}賢者
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.31,0:13:26.33,Default,,0,0,0,,那是因為...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.33,0:13:29.42,Default,,0,0,0,,我有耳聞 那個叫Zero Two的雌式
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.33,0:13:29.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs40\pos(1395,980)}Pistil
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.42,0:13:33.22,Default,,0,0,0,,好像擁有能獨自啟動FRANXX的特殊體質
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.22,0:13:36.66,Default,,0,0,0,,兩位也看見了吧 那時它四腳著地的型態
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.22,0:13:36.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs40\pos(1038.4,980)}鶴望蘭
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.66,0:13:40.75,Default,,0,0,0,,也就是說廣只是單純的坐在裡面 毫無作為罷了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.06,0:13:45.40,Default,,0,0,0,,你看吧 我絕不承認他已經領先我們了的這件事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.88,0:13:51.75,Default,,0,0,0,,少在那給我得意忘形了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.28,0:13:56.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs40\pos(712,980)}BINGO
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.28,0:13:56.82,Default,,0,0,0,,賓果 本大爺超強的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.82,0:14:00.71,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉抱歉 我以為你躲的開的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.95,0:14:04.44,Default,,0,0,0,,一個人偷偷地用訓練機練習嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.53,0:14:06.48,Default,,0,0,0,,很符合你的作風呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.48,0:14:10.51,Default,,0,0,0,,只會靠女生 什麼事都辦不到的愛哭鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.91,0:14:14.11,Default,,0,0,0,,怎樣 想打架嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.11,0:14:16.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Zero Two她說了 是我操縱的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.37,0:14:18.73,Default,,0,0,0,,訓練機和實機可不一樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.73,0:14:21.33,Default,,0,0,0,,要是能再上去一次我就操縱給你看
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.53,0:14:24.40,Default,,0,0,0,,正合我意
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.40,0:14:26.28,Default,,0,0,0,,等等 你們在幹嘛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.15,0:14:29.28,Default,,0,0,0,,不要這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.28,0:14:30.66,Default,,0,0,0,,別妨礙我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.66,0:14:31.77,Default,,0,0,0,,喂 別激動
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.77,0:14:34.44,Default,,0,0,0,,混帳 你這傢伙 明明只是個不適任者
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.08,0:14:33.40,Background,,0,0,0,,冷靜一點
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.44,0:14:35.95,Default,,0,0,0,,不用太在意他說的沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.20,0:14:38.42,Background,,0,0,0,,放開我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.66,0:14:39.82,Default,,0,0,0,,只要給我機會證明的話...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.88,0:14:41.84,Default,,0,0,0,,廣...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.53,0:14:45.75,Default,,0,0,0,,七姐打來的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.95,0:14:49.06,Default,,0,0,0,,讓我操縱實機進行模擬戰?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.17,0:14:50.48,Default,,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.60,0:14:54.13,Default,,0,0,0,,根據結果而定 或許有機會成為正式操縱者
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.60,0:14:54.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs40\pos(1476.8,980)}Parasite
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.28,0:14:56.22,Default,,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.71,0:14:57.68,Default,,0,0,0,,那麼 關於搭檔
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.68,0:14:58.91,Default,,0,0,0,,讓我來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.40,0:15:00.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Zero Two
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.91,0:15:03.97,Default,,0,0,0,,畢竟 你是我的Darling不是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.15,0:15:05.31,Default,,0,0,0,,請等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.75,0:15:07.75,Default,,0,0,0,,搭檔請由我來擔任
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.75,0:15:08.66,Default,,0,0,0,,莓
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.86,0:15:11.60,Default,,0,0,0,,她並不是我們隊伍的成員
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.86,0:15:11.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs40\pos(625.6,980)}002
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.68,0:15:12.53,Default,,0,0,0,,而且
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.53,0:15:14.22,Default,,0,0,0,,以和廣的適性來說
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.22,0:15:16.35,Default,,0,0,0,,作為搭檔我是足以勝任的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.42,0:15:18.95,Default,,0,0,0,,即便如此 也沒有必要讓莓擔任吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.95,0:15:22.04,Default,,0,0,0,,首先 她也有五郎這個搭檔了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.04,0:15:23.57,Default,,0,0,0,,現在還多了廣要配合嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.57,0:15:26.68,Default,,0,0,0,,那邊的 不要擅自發言
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.11,0:15:28.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Zero Two
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.13,0:15:31.40,Default,,0,0,0,,本部沒有傳來鶴望蘭的啟動許可
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.46,0:15:33.57,Default,,0,0,0,,所以這次的測驗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.57,0:15:35.91,Default,,0,0,0,,廣得從他們之中選出一個來配合才行
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.28,0:15:39.02,Default,,0,0,0,,什麼嘛 真無趣
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.13,0:15:42.73,Default,,0,0,0,,也好 反正之前的傷還沒痊癒
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.35,0:15:44.33,Default,,0,0,0,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.60,0:15:47.26,Default,,0,0,0,,那這次就讓給妳吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.26,0:15:49.02,Default,,0,0,0,,讓妳體驗一下也好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.73,0:15:51.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Darling就拜託妳囉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.37,0:15:53.53,Default,,0,0,0,,那麼 莓
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.55,0:15:54.73,Default,,0,0,0,,交給妳了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.95,0:15:55.75,Default,,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.13,0:15:57.15,Default,,0,0,0,,慢著
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.82,0:16:00.71,Default,,0,0,0,,那麼 作為實戰演練的對手
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.71,0:16:01.46,Default,,0,0,0,,我!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.80,0:16:03.86,Default,,0,0,0,,等等 幹嘛擅自決定啦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.86,0:16:07.17,Default,,0,0,0,,我要讓他們看看本大爺我的實力
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.68,0:16:09.60,Default,,0,0,0,,我也加入
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.60,0:16:10.48,Default,,0,0,0,,沒問題了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.48,0:16:12.11,Default,,0,0,0,,模擬戰預計於明早舉行
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.11,0:16:13.46,Default,,0,0,0,,我我我!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.46,0:16:15.48,Default,,0,0,0,,我提議即刻開始舉行
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.44,0:16:17.82,Default,,0,0,0,,揃目他啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.82,0:16:19.73,Default,,0,0,0,,對白天的事還再耿耿於懷吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.11,0:16:21.06,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.06,0:16:23.37,Default,,0,0,0,,莓明明是你的搭檔
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.62,0:16:26.08,Default,,0,0,0,,那邊好像準備好了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.37,0:16:28.28,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 那我去去就回
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.28,0:16:29.82,Default,,0,0,0,,待會見啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.95,0:16:31.88,Default,,0,0,0,,廣 不用太在意
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.06,0:16:34.75,Default,,0,0,0,,她一旦說出口的事 就沒人能改變了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.11,0:16:38.42,Default,,0,0,0,,我會好好把握這個機會的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.42,0:16:41.15,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 你一定沒問題的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.04,0:16:50.48,Default,,0,0,0,,喂 你這愛哭鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.48,0:16:52.64,Default,,0,0,0,,這次就讓你明白我們之間的差距
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.66,0:16:55.84,Default,,0,0,0,,和那傢伙搭檔 即使是優秀的隊長大人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.84,0:16:57.00,Default,,0,0,0,,搞不好我也能獲勝唷
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.00,0:16:58.35,Default,,0,0,0,,請自便吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.35,0:17:00.53,Default,,0,0,0,,先提醒妳 模擬戰可沒有輸贏之分
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.57,0:17:02.91,Default,,0,0,0,,未來也幹勁十足呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.11,0:17:04.53,Default,,0,0,0,,這不是輸贏的問題
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.84,0:17:06.82,Default,,0,0,0,,廣依然能夠操縱FRANXX這件事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.82,0:17:08.53,Default,,0,0,0,,得由我來證明!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.55,0:17:11.68,Default,,0,0,0,,廣只要專心在連結上就好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.97,0:17:14.02,Default,,0,0,0,,其他的事都交給我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.11,0:17:15.02,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.60,0:17:17.31,Default,,0,0,0,,那麼 模擬戰 開始
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.62,0:17:21.40,Default,,0,0,0,,我隨時都可以上了唷
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.68,0:17:22.93,Default,,0,0,0,,集中精神
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.40,0:17:25.53,Default,,0,0,0,,沒問題
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.55,0:17:28.08,Default,,0,0,0,,我一定可以喚醒廣的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.22,0:17:31.60,Default,,0,0,0,,這種感覺...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.26,0:17:35.75,Default,,0,0,0,,我進入了莓的意識中?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.68,0:17:39.08,Default,,0,0,0,,放心吧 保持這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.44,0:17:40.57,Default,,0,0,0,,連結上了!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.17,0:17:50.42,Default,,0,0,0,,真的假的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.64,0:17:51.53,Default,,0,0,0,,成功了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.86,0:17:53.31,Default,,0,0,0,,太好了 廣
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.88,0:17:54.77,Default,,0,0,0,,不過呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.15,0:17:58.80,Default,,0,0,0,,現在開始才是問題所在
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.86,0:18:00.15,Default,,0,0,0,,我有印象
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.15,0:18:01.53,Default,,0,0,0,,就是這種感覺
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.53,0:18:02.88,Default,,0,0,0,,要上囉 廣
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.88,0:18:03.66,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.28,0:18:09.51,Default,,0,0,0,,好樣的 來啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.51,0:18:10.40,Default,,0,0,0,,什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.51,0:18:14.42,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.97,0:18:16.02,Default,,0,0,0,,停止運轉了?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.57,0:18:18.71,Default,,0,0,0,,為 為什麼...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.24,0:18:21.44,Default,,0,0,0,,發生這種事...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.35,0:18:23.37,Default,,0,0,0,,暫停!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.37,0:18:24.46,Default,,0,0,0,,給我三分鐘
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.46,0:18:25.42,Default,,0,0,0,,啥!?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.22,0:18:27.84,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼可以擅自...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.93,0:18:29.06,Default,,0,0,0,,為什麼突然...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.06,0:18:30.57,Default,,0,0,0,,動啊! 快動啊!!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.68,0:18:32.68,Default,,0,0,0,,可惡 不可能的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.80,0:18:34.82,Default,,0,0,0,,那個時候明明可以操縱的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.75,0:18:38.82,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼了?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.82,0:18:40.71,Default,,0,0,0,,我不知道 突然就...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.33,0:18:42.66,Default,,0,0,0,,是因為我的關係嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.66,0:18:44.24,Default,,0,0,0,,我想不是...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.48,0:18:47.15,Default,,0,0,0,,和跟她操縱時 有哪裡不同嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.48,0:18:47.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs40\pos(692,980)}002
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.15,0:18:50.06,Default,,0,0,0,,不知道...我記不起來
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.28,0:18:51.33,Default,,0,0,0,,先冷靜下來
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.33,0:18:52.22,Default,,0,0,0,,不要急
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.22,0:18:54.17,Default,,0,0,0,,或許就會想起些什麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.57,0:18:59.57,Default,,0,0,0,,接吻...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.84,0:19:00.51,Default,,0,0,0,,咦?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.62,0:19:02.77,Default,,0,0,0,,搞不好是因為 接吻
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.80,0:19:04.73,Default,,0,0,0,,接吻 那是什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.82,0:19:07.44,Default,,0,0,0,,兩個人 嘴唇交疊在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.55,0:19:10.57,Default,,0,0,0,,然後眼前出現強光 啪的一聲
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.20,0:19:16.28,Default,,0,0,0,,是怎樣 那種情況下 你們還在做那種事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.28,0:19:17.75,Default,,0,0,0,,不是我做的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.75,0:19:20.17,Default,,0,0,0,,是我在搭上去時她突然就...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.64,0:19:21.53,Default,,0,0,0,,就連我
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.53,0:19:23.53,Default,,0,0,0,,到現在還是不懂那有什麼涵義
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.62,0:19:26.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Zero Two只說了是很特別的事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.73,0:19:38.55,Default,,0,0,0,,我明白了 來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.08,0:19:40.88,Default,,0,0,0,,但我會不好意思 所以你把眼睛閉上
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.88,0:19:42.02,Default,,0,0,0,,等 等等
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.02,0:19:43.68,Default,,0,0,0,,不這樣做就無法啟動不是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.13,0:19:47.15,Default,,0,0,0,,如果是為了啟動 這點小事不算什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.13,0:19:47.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs40\pos(849.6,980)}證明
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.17,0:19:48.97,Default,,0,0,0,,可是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.97,0:19:50.02,Default,,0,0,0,,別說話
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.26,0:19:52.57,Default,,0,0,0,,莓 可是妳在發抖...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.97,0:19:59.02,Default,,0,0,0,,哎 超過三分鐘了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.02,0:20:02.11,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊 我們也算仁至義盡了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.77,0:20:07.33,Default,,0,0,0,,雖然很過意不去 不過就讓我來作結吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.02,0:20:15.91,Default,,0,0,0,,如何?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.11,0:20:22.64,Default,,0,0,0,,沒有...任何感覺...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.24,0:20:25.26,Default,,0,0,0,,行不通...的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.13,0:20:36.68,Default,,0,0,0,,喂喂 太無趣了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.77,0:20:39.02,Default,,0,0,0,,廣 再試一次
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.46,0:20:45.11,Default,,0,0,0,,果然 本大爺我才是最強的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.31,0:20:50.00,Default,,0,0,0,,既然如此 乾脆讓本大爺來操控那台翠雀吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.31,0:20:50.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs40\pos(1440,980)}Delphinium
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.00,0:20:50.97,Default,,0,0,0,,啥
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.97,0:20:53.00,Default,,0,0,0,,都這個節骨眼了還再搭訕?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.00,0:20:55.04,Default,,0,0,0,,你也該適可而止了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.64,0:21:02.53,Default,,0,0,0,,咦?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.60,0:21:05.84,Default,,0,0,0,,搭檔間的信賴關係
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.93,0:21:08.20,Default,,0,0,0,,會直接反映在操縱的靈敏度上
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.37,0:21:10.46,Default,,0,0,0,,當平衡一旦瓦解
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.71,0:21:13.44,Default,,0,0,0,,發生什麼事了 突然就...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.66,0:21:18.84,Default,,0,0,0,,莓 回報現況
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.84,0:21:19.68,Default,,0,0,0,,莓?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.95,0:21:24.13,Default,,0,0,0,,快點起身啦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.13,0:21:25.60,Default,,0,0,0,,吵死了 我在試了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.40,0:21:27.44,Default,,0,0,0,,不行! 莓
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.57,0:21:29.93,Default,,0,0,0,,只靠妳一個人啟動太危險了!!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.11,0:21:35.46,Default,,0,0,0,,可惡!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.42,0:21:46.22,Default,,0,0,0,,真是有夠亂來的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.28,0:21:50.57,Default,,0,0,0,,雙方都無法動作 模擬戰到此為止
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.55,0:21:59.62,Default,,0,0,0,,顫抖的雙唇 伴隨著柔軟的觸感及罪惡感
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.20,0:22:02.51,Default,,0,0,0,,那時 一度以為自己能飛上藍天的感覺
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.73,0:22:04.71,Default,,0,0,0,,自指間不斷的流逝
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.93,0:22:08.44,Default,,0,0,0,,我終究還是...被束縛在地表
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.60,0:22:14.71,Default,,0,0,0,,沒錯 就像是 全身被無形的線錯縱纏繞般
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.68,0:22:17.66,Default,,0,0,0,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.13,0:22:20.35,Default,,0,0,0,,你不用道歉...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.93,0:22:31.00,Default,,0,0,0,,是我太沒用
